    "causal_summary": "This sub-phase hardens soft spot B, envelope fidelity, the robustness gap the 029 benchmark surfaced alongside the off-corpus false-positive. The memory-search tool always ships the requestQuality and citationPolicy verdict on a non-empty result and the verdict is correct, but the render contract lets a weaker model drop the two fields, so the verdict is model-dependently absent. The phase reclassifies the fields to conditionally-mandatory render slots, adds a deterministic post-render fidelity check that replays the tool verdict against the rendered block, and emits a pre-rendered verdict fragment so the model pastes rather than transcribes. Every behavioral change ships behind a default-OFF flag or a grandfather report mode because the existing renders carry the looser absence-is-valid contract the new mandate rejects, so enforcement graduates only after a clean grandfather report.",
